data.description: Tons of space & character throughout this well designed home with vaulted wood ceilings & floor to ceiling stone fireplace in living room. The chef's kitchen is ideally situated next to formal dining room with granite counters, convenient eating bar, and easy access to  pantry and back deck for barbecuing. Enjoy the private views from the Primary Suite which also is accessible to the deck.  Primary Bath features separate sinks, large additional vanity area, large tiled jetted bath tub & separate shower.  All 2 acres been well manicured with circular driveway separating front lawn and ample room for parking RV or boats on side. House has brand new roof and solar for huge savings with the pending increases coming for PG&E electric bills.
